= HostBot: your Wikipedia robot friend =
[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:HostBot HostBot] is a set of Python scripts that performs repetitive tasks on and for the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Teahouse Wikipedia Teahouse]. HostBot is run by [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Jtmorgan Jonathan Morgan], and is hosted on [https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Main_Page Wikimedia Labs].

Information about what the Teahouse is, and how it came to be can be found [http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Teahouse here]. If you're interested in creating a Teahouse on your home wiki, please email Jonathan or post to [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Jtmorgan his talk page on Wikipedia].

== Functions ==

=== Talk page invitations ===
Posts invitations to visit the Teahouse to the talk pages of new Wikipedia editors.

